(52, 12, 'The Lord of the Ring', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//vRQnzOn4HjIMX4LBq9nHhFXbsSu.jpg', 'movie', 'Released', '2001-12-18', 17245, 8, 'Young hobbit Frodo Baggins, after inheriting a mysterious ring from his uncle Bilbo, must leave his home in order to keep it from falling into the hands of its evil creator. Along the way, a fellowship is formed to protect the ringbearer and make sure tha', 178, ''),
