(55, 99, 'Dworzec', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/', 'movie', 'Released', '1980-01-01', 14, 6, 'Railway Station is a documentary about a Warsaw railway station Dworzec that was controversial and against the government at the time. The footage that exposed the monitoring of sales was seized by police', 13, ''),
